title: Spacious 9' ceilings, Stylish private cabanas, Ceiling fans included

posting_body: ['Schedule a Tour Today: <URL>', 'Discover a life of ease at Palmetto Promenade.', 'At our luxury apartments in Boca Raton, residents will find a selection of one bedroom, two bedroom, and three bedroom homes that are sure to suit any lifestyle.', 'In each home, residents will enjoy the chef-caliber kitchens with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances, private balconies, and spacious closets with built-in shelving.', 'Throughout the community at our Boca apartments, residents can take advantage of the resort-style swimming pool with private cabanas, cutting-edge fitness center, and the outdoor entertainment area.', 'Amenities:', '-Ceiling fans included', '-Professional concierge services available', '-Washer and dryer in every residence', '-Walk-out balconies and large terraces available', '-Individually controlled heating and air conditioning with Nest thermostats', '-51-bottle wine cooler in most residences', '-Summer kitchen pavilion including grills, pizza oven and refrigeration', '-Modern one, two and three bedroom residences', '-Resort-style landscaping and water features surround the community', '-Electric car charging stations', '-Powder rooms in select residences', '-Amazing views of Boca Raton, the Boca Raton Country Club and beaches from upper level residences', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
